seq:A000240_F_1_20250105T195131 a seq:Text ;
    cnt:chars """E.g.f.: x*exp(-x)/(1-x). [Corrected by _Vaclav Kotesovec_, Sep 26 2012]
a(n) = Sum_{k=0..n-1} (-1)^k*n!/k!.
a(n) = A180188(n,0). - _Emeric Deutsch_, Sep 06 2010
E.g.f.: x*A(x) where A(x) is the e.g.f. for A000166. - _Geoffrey Critzer_, Jan 14 2012
a(n) = n*a(n-1) - (-1)^n*n = A000166(n) - (-1)^n = n*A000166(n-1) = A000387(n+1)*2/(n+1) = A000449(n+2)*6/((n+1)*(n+2)).
a(n) = n*floor(((n-1)!+1)/e), n > 1. - _Gary Detlefs_, Jul 13 2010
Limit_{n->infinity} n!/a(n) = e = 2.71828...
a(n) = (n-1)*(a(n-1)+a(n-2)) + (-1)^(n-1), n>=2. - _Enrique Navarrete_, Oct 07 2016
O.g.f.: Sum_{k>=1} k!*x^k/(1 + x)^(k+1). - _Ilya Gutkovskiy_, Apr 13 2017
a(n) = (-1)^(n-1)*n*hypergeom([1,1-n], [], 1). - _Peter Luschny_, May 09 2017"""@en .

